,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"貼上 我愛民主，還比你呀何妖<br />\n剃佢頭，除褲抬高送佢出去，"},{"pid":"aaf0209e2b8156731a91b073159838ca1901cfaa","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"35a37e84be1f6b2b5ded0713ca23e9906ab2fbb5","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"269cdf036924225ce42fd8c5b12e8956c84fb102","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7110a5d92973f1cf04acad67e3fb070d45726e86","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d1d82ad103228a30f8dd370bca3c7d9e908e6dd2","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d8e88012e62525fa89daa483f9274a06a2180d91","tid":1466761,"uid":16073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"不割"},{"pid":"a8066fce2d35f525e53f073e45bc85db48792b5a","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5f780642dcf647765ebed79ff806b1814df9aa8d","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:45.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"16c3a99fea28cd77d17dd2013212e5bc2d108929","tid":1466761,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"同路人走人都掉口罩頭盔<br />\n<br />\n明知機場有對家 都袋撐警衫扮記者<br />\n<br />\n環時記者只係表面身份 中共指派邊個都可以係<br />\n<br />\n實情扮可疑 引你追 再引你搜袋 出手打人<br />\n<br />\n一般人比咁多人圍住兇會咁冷靜？明明咩都係中國但對鏡頭淨係講英文<br />\n<br />\n中共特務黎架"},{"pid":"da0aabf8717bfd422269b6a0b368725dc6890fd5","tid":1466761,"uid":211467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a30d4a0df8d949e4747